content.text: Inspired by glitch art and the Max Headroom-ness of the process, I'm showing various manipulations of the bust where I've pulled apart pieces of my head in a digital fashion, made real, and made digital again for this gallery. For every piece, they look whole from a certain angle, but in the movement panning around the object, we see their distortion.
